ds_pinyin_lsp:
https://github.com/iamcco/ds-pinyin-lsp Dead simple Pinyin language
server for input Chinese without IME(input method). To install, download
the latest [release](https://github.com/iamcco/ds-pinyin-lsp/releases)
and ensure `ds-pinyin-lsp` is on your path. And make ensure the database
file `dict.db3` is also downloaded. And put the path to `dict.dbs` in
the following code.

``` lua
vim.lsp.config('ds_pinyin_lsp', {
    init_options = {
        db_path = "your_path_to_database"
    }
})
```

